{"tid":819201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[Not ifc]男子中環商廈墮樓　壓排檔頂反彈落地重傷亡","createTime":"2018-09-14T15:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T07:32:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5da841df926612246c1236af937b770dab19683b","tid":819201,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:26:12.000Z","msg":"中環發生男子墮樓死亡案，現場為利源東街9號，今晚（14日）9時許，一名38歲男子由附近一座商業大廈高處墮下，先壓毀排檔的鋅鐵板再反彈落地，頭爆肢折，保安員發現後即時報案。警方及救護員接報到場，證實男子已當場死亡，遂用帳篷將遺體遮蓋，警方在其身上尋獲一部手機及身份證明文件，正嘗試聯絡其家人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180914/photo/bkn-20180914213727379-0914_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180914231847\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180914%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180914213727379-0914_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180914231847&h=c94d06f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180914/bkn-20180914213727379-0914_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180914%2Fbkn-20180914213727379-0914_00822_001.html&d=alc6ADMhWDFEza5vL8L7ogRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=be241b15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180914/bkn-20180914213727379-0914_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c142a5b48bada2d6bddafc9fa8a0ddcc70538624","tid":819201,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"股海亡魂"},{"pid":"a124503401d190ff1ced3db4fbc6a43c00cd5e12","tid":819201,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"孖展買熊，但個市反彈，夾爆左？"},{"pid":"a0382e2b2f1e374aa4f71d05c834dba7c3f16910","tid":819201,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:03:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ada4f979d00b368ae4f1f0611aafe685a349014d","tid":819201,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"前面有間慢煮燒味好好食"},{